      "heading": "Our vision and values",
      "lede": "Rosehill College will nurture a culture of excellence through Hihiritanga, Rangatiratanga, Whanaungatanga, and Manaakitanga.",
      "values": [
        {
          "reo": "Manaakitanga",
          "english": "Connect",
          "meaning": "\"We rise by lifting others.\" We use mana-enhancing, respectful, inclusive words and actions, and look after our learning environment.",
