      "type": "home-journey",
      "eyebrow": "Te haerenga",
      "reo": true,
      "heading": "The journey — Year 9 to Year 13",
      "lede": "Five years, one pathway. From your first day to your last, every step at Rosehill College builds towards personal excellence.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "year": "9",
          "title": "Settle in and belong",
          "text": "Your Junior Diploma journey begins — our in-house qualification recognising participation, effort and achievement across all aspects of school life — alongside the SMART assessment in literacy and numeracy.",
          "link": {
            "href": "/curriculum/year-9-smart-assessment.html",
            "label": "Year 9 SMART Assessment"
          },
          "image": {
            "src": "assets/img/Junior-Diploma-2.avif",
            "srcset": "",
            "alt": "A Rosehill College junior student at a school celebration"
          }
        },
        {
          "year": "10",
          "title": "Build your foundations",
          "text": "The Junior Diploma continues, building foundational skills in literacy and numeracy while you explore a wide variety of subjects — and head beyond the classroom on Year 10 camp.",
          "link": {
            "href": "/curriculum/junior-diploma.html",
            "label": "Junior Diploma"
          },
          "image": {
            "src": "assets/img/Year-10-Camp_1.avif",
            "srcset": "",
            "alt": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "year": "11",
          "title": "Step up",
          "text": "The final year of the Junior Diploma — awarded at Achieved, Merit or Excellence — sharpens your goals and readies you for NCEA study in the senior school.",
          "link": {
            "href": "/curriculum/course-information.html",
            "label": "Course information"
          },
          "image": {
            "src": "assets/img/Junior-Diploma-1.avif",
            "srcset": "",
            "alt": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "year": "12",
          "title": "Specialise",
          "text": "NCEA Level 2 and specialised senior courses let you tailor your education to your strengths — with leadership roles opening across sport, arts, culture and service.",
          "link": {
            "href": "/curriculum/course-information.html",
            "label": "Senior courses"
          },
          "image": {
            "src": "assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance.avif",
            "srcset": "/assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance-rp-500.avif 500w, /assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance-rp-800.avif 800w, /assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance-rp-1080.avif 1080w, /assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance-rp-1600.avif 1600w, /assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance-rp-2200.avif 2200w, /assets/img/RHC-Cultural-Performance.avif 2344w",
